name: Centralize Login-Authentication via Cogntio controlled by Ambassador Edge Stack
about: Decouple the authentication from mono into its own service. This will allow for a simpler code base and a much more customization UI while being resilient from any mono/ui downtown. This will also enable other teams to not have to worry about re implementing JWT or OAUTH as we can forward the headers to the downstream service after initial authentication.
